       Everything is gated on the NuGet package being restored, so a checkout without
       it builds byte-for-byte unchanged. Restore the package (packages.config) to
       light up NEURON_USE_PIX in the x64 configs. -->
  <PropertyGroup Label="NeuronPix">
    <NeuronPixRoot>$(SolutionDir)packages\WinPixEventRuntime.1.0.240308001</NeuronPixRoot>
